steps.instruction:
### Spices
- In a small bowl, combine brown sugar, paprika, salt, mustard, pepper, thyme and garlic powder
- Drink or pour out half of the tall boy, add 1 teaspoon of the spice mixture to the can

### Chicken
- Remove neck and giblets from chicken
- Sprinkle 1 teaspoon of the spice mixture inside of the cavity
- Rub the outside of the chicken with butter and sprinkle the remaining spices
- Hold the chicken upright and put the can inside the cavity of the chicken
- Pull the legs forward so the chicken rests on the can and legs
- Twist the wings behind the back of the chicken 
- Stuff the lemon wedge in the neck cavity

### Cooking
- Preheat grill then reduce to medium heat
- Turn one of the burners off so you can do indirect cooking
- Put chicken onto the turned off side of the grill
- Cook for 1.25 to 1.75 hours or until it hit 180F in the thigh
- Remove from grill and cover with foil, let stand for 10 minutes
